It's about time! = It's later than expected! 생각보다 늦었네.
be in love (with someone) = love (someo ne) strongly in a romantic way. 사랑에 빠졌다.
get married (to someone) = marry (someone) 누구와 결혼하다.
can afford something = have enough money to buy something 금전적으로 여유로운.
cost an arm and a leg = be very expensive 너어무 비싼.
save up = keep money so one can use it later 저축하다.
at long last =  after a very long time; finally 오랜 시간끝에
tie the knot = marry 결혼.
be in seventh heaven = be very happy 너무 행복한